The System:

	PlacingOntology - Spatial and Temporal
			- [Output]	Person IsStillIn Room
			- [Output]	Person IsBeingIn Room
			- [Input]	From MySQl DB

	TaskOntology2	- Spatial and Temporal
			- [Output]	Person IsDoingActivity Activity (WatchingTV)
			- [Input]	Person IsStillIn Room (LivingRoom)

	TaskOntology3	- Spatial and Temporal
			- [Output]	Person IsDoingActivity Activity (MakingBreakfast/Lunch/Dinner)
			- [Input]	Person IsStillIn Room (Kitchen)

	TaskOntology4	- Spatial and Temporal
			- [Output]	Person IsDoingActivity Activity (EatingBreakfast/Lunch/Dinner)
			- [Input]	Person IsStillIn Room (AnyRoom other than BathRoom)
			- [Input]	Person isOccupying Furniture (Some furniture in that Room)
			- [Input]	Person hasPosture Sitting
			- [Input]	After Making()/()/()
